    {
        "content": "<p>Relevant references on this topic:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\"A characterization of pie limits\" by Power and Robinson. See Definition 1.7, and the description of the universal property of products on page 37 of the pdf.</li>\n<li>\"Elementary observations on 2-categorical limits\" by Kelly. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note: both papers are about the strict version.</p>",
        "id": 348514033,
        "sender_full_name": "Niels van der Weide",
        "timestamp": 1681231527
    },
